{"title_page": "Delaware\u2013William & Mary football rivalry", "text_new": "{{Use mdy dates|date=December 2013}}\n{{Infobox sports rivalry\n| wide                  = yes\n| name                  = Delaware\u2013William & Mary football rivalry\n| image                 = \n| image_size            = \n| caption               = \n| team1                 = [[Delaware Fightin' Blue Hens football|Delaware Fightin' Blue Hens]]\n| team1logo             = Delaware Football wordmark.svg\n| team2                 = [[William & Mary Tribe football|William & Mary Tribe]]\n| team2logo             = William and Mary Tribe wordmark.svg\n| sport                 = [[College football]]\n| firstmeeting          = November 25, 1915<br />Delaware 93, William & Mary 0\n| mostrecent            = October 14, 2017<br />Delaware 17, William & Mary 0\n| nextmeeting           = October 24, 2020\n| total                 = 42\n| series                = Delaware leads, 24\u201318\n| largestvictory        = Delaware, 93\u20130 (1915)\n| longeststreak         = Delaware, 5 (1976\u20131983)\n| longestunbeatenstreak = \n| currentstreak         = Delaware, 1 (2017\u2013present)\n| currentunbeatenstreak = \n| trophy                = \n| trophy series         = \n| stadiums              =  \n}}\n{{OSM Location map       \n| coord = {{coord|38.428|-76.229}}\n| nolabels = 1\n| zoom = 6\n| width = 295 \n| height = 250\n| caption = Locations of Delaware and William & Mary\n| mark1 = Blue pog.svg\n| label1 = Delaware\n| mark-coord1 = {{coord|39.679|-75.752}}\n| label-pos1 = left\n| label-color1 = black\n| mark2 = Green pog.svg\n| label2 = William & Mary\n| mark-coord2 = {{coord|37.271|-76.707}}\n| label-pos2 = left\n| label-color2 = black\n}}\n\nThe '''Delaware\u2013William & Mary football rivalry''' <ref>{{cite web|publisher=DailyPress.com|url=http://articles.dailypress.com/2011-10-08/sports/dp-spt-william-mary-delaware-20111008_1_nihja-white-blue-hens-tribe-coach-jimmye-laycock |date=October 8, 2011 |work=Daily Press|accessdate=November 2, 2013 |title=QBs flat again, William and Mary loses to Delaware 21-0}}</ref> between the [[Delaware Fightin' Blue Hens football|Delaware Fightin' Blue Hens]] and the [[William & Mary Tribe football|William & Mary Tribe]] is a match-up between two public universities, the [[University of Delaware]] and the [[College of William and Mary]], that are also members of the [[Colonial Athletic Association]]. Both schools have academic reputations that have labeled them as [[Public Ivies]]. Both schools are also [[Colonial Colleges]] having been founded before the United States became independent in 1776; the [[College of William and Mary]] was founded in 1693 and the [[University of Delaware]]'s predecessor school was founded in 1743.\n\nThe football series began in 1915 and has been played a total of 42 times as of 2017.\n\n==History==\nPreviously, the game has been a divisional game in the CAA South, and conference game in the [[Yankee Conference]] and [[Atlantic 10]] beginning with the Tribe's entry in 1993. During this period, the two teams have combined for one National Championship (Delaware in 2003), two shared Conference Championships (2004 and 2010) and seven standalone conference titles (Delaware in 1995, 2000, 2003, and 2010 and William & Mary in 1996 and 2001).<ref>{{cite web|title=2013 CAA Football Media Guide|url=http://www.caasports.com/fls/8500/FBMedia/13Guide/YBY_Standings_77_80.pdf?DB_OEM_ID=8500|publisher=Colonial Athletic Association|accessdate=November 30, 2013}}</ref> With the exception of the 1915 game held at [[Frazer Field]], all of Delaware's home games have been hosted at [[Delaware Stadium]] in [[Newark, Delaware]]. William & Mary has hosted its contests at [[Zable Stadium]] in [[Williamsburg, Virginia]]; as of 2019, no games have been played on a neutral field.\n\n==Game results==\n{{sports rivalry series table\n| series_summary = yes\n| legend_tie_text = \n| format = compact | cols = 2\n| team1 = Delaware\n| team